channel.title: Ipl0x is dieing
channel.description:
Well guys/girls I gave up on Java when I got to the last free lesson Greasley posted, I can't stand learning from a book takes for ever to remember every code and whatever they try teaching from books. Another reason I gave up was cause I work all day, get up at 7:00 am and get home at around 6:00 to 8:00 pm. To get to the point, I'll only be able to visit these forums [b]very[/b] rarely, also I'll start at my Java skills again but I'll have [b]very[/b] little progress since not enough time for me to get anything memorized.
Thanks to the guys who gave me all the help I needed, your ownage.
I'll be able to get on for long periods of time when school starts but that's like in August 30th for me, not sure exactly when, and I also got Running Start for Community College in September 1st, not sure when exactly when. So I hope I'll get enough time to get any progress in anything.
Peace guy's/girls.
PS: My request is that I wouldn't like to get banned for inactivity, I gave you the reason above, ty.
